                       Saint Guide v1.13 (95-05-13)
                       ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{b}Saint Guide@{ub} was programmed by Torbjörn Hansson. It is Public Domain and may
by freely distributated.


   @{"  Introduction     " link "intro"} - Why this silly utility?
   @{"  Requirements     " link "requirements"} - Will it work on my system?
   @{"  How To Edit      " link "howtoedit"} - How do I edit my SGuidefiles?
   @{"  Usage            " link "usage"} - How do I use SGuide?

   @{"  Info & Credits   " link "credits"} - Who did this shit?
